converstationContexts: 欢迎来到奇妙大陆，点击这里，进入你的第一场战斗吧！
Welcome to Wonderland, click to enter your first battle!
选择关卡，进入战斗！
Choose a level and enter the battle!
在战斗中，敌人会不断的从上方城门出现，并朝我方大本营进攻。
During battle, the enemy will continue to appear from the upper city gate and attack our base camp.
这里会显示我方大本营所能承受的敌军数量。
This will show the number of enemy troops that our base camp can withstand.
注意左上角的胜利条件，这是你的第一场战斗，只要成功抵挡敌人的入侵即可获胜！
Pay attention to the victory condition in the upper left corner, resist the enemy's invasion and win!
点击这里，招募一位英雄吧！
Click here to recruit a hero!
点击大剑士的头像。
Click the avatar of Swordsman.
敌人数量较多，单靠一个英雄的力量很难阻挡所有敌军
Large enemies, and it is difficult to stop all enemy with single hero strength
点击这里，再招募一名大剑士吧！
Click here to recruit another Swordsman!
选择剑士
Pick Swordsman
战斗中招募单位会消耗银币。
Recruiting units in battle will consume silver coins.
银币可以通过击败敌军获得，但只能在本次战斗中使用，请无所保留的挥霍吧！
Silver coins can be obtained by defeating the enemy, but they can only be used in this battle, please squander it without reservation!
战斗胜利！领取你的报酬，回到主城吧！
WIN! Receive your reward and return to the main city!
在这里签到
Sign-in here
打开签到二级面板
Open sign-in secondary panel
领取签到奖励
Receive rewards
签到可以获得大量奖励，每日一次，不要忘了领取哦！
You can get a lot of rewards by sign-in, once a day!
关闭签到面板
Close
现在我们已经有了一定的资金，去招募新英雄吧！
Now recruit new heroes!
选择英雄界面
Select Hero
手上的金币足够，点击这里，解锁新英雄！
Cick here to unlock new heroes!
选择英雄界面
Select Hero
点击火枪
Click Gun
点击升级，提升火枪手的等级！
Click to upgrade Musketeer!
选择英雄界面
Select Hero
点击火枪
Click Gun
点击“技能”选项，可以查看每个英雄拥有的技能。
Click the "Skills" option to view the skills each hero possesses.
火枪手的技能使他更容易触发暴击，现在就为他升级技能吧。
Musketeer's skills make him more likely to trigger critical strikes, so upgrade his skills now.
关闭英雄详情
Close
点击这里回到世界
Click here to go back to the world
进入关卡
Enter Level
开始新的一关
Start new level
本关的战斗条件有了新的变化。
The combat conditions of this level have new changes.
英雄是无法攻击城门的，这时就轮到士兵登场了！
Heroes can't attack the city gates, so it's the soldiers' turn to come on stage!
点击这里打开兵营选单
Click to open the barracks
选择步兵兵营
Select Infantry Barracks
兵营每隔一段时间会招募新的士兵加入你的队伍。
The barracks will recruit new soldiers to join your team every once in a while.
士兵不仅会抵挡敌军，也会向敌方发动攻击。
Soldiers will not only resist the enemy, but also attack the enemy.
未经训练的士兵战斗力还不高，让我们招募一名火枪手帮助他们吧！
Untrained soldiers are not very effective, let's recruit a musketeer to help them!
指引造火枪手
Guide musketeer
战斗胜利！
WIN!
点击这里进入兵营
Click to enter Barracks
先给步兵兵营升级吧！
Upgrade Infantry Barracks!
升级兵营不止可以提升对应士兵的属性，还可以加快战斗中士兵的训练速度！
Upgrading the barracks can not only improve the attributes of the corresponding soldiers, but also speed up the training speed of soldiers in battle!
让我们再次开始战斗吧!
Let's fighting again!
进入第三关！
Enter level.3!
进入第三关！
Enter level.3!
本关不止要防御敌军的进攻，还要与敌人进行决战。
This level is not only to defend against the enemy's attack, but also to have a decisive battle with the enemy.
在防守阶段布置的英雄都会在决战阶段登场。
The heroes deployed in the defense phase will appear in the final battle phase.
兵营也会转换成对应的5名士兵加入决战。
The barracks will also be converted into corresponding 5 soldiers to join the decisive battle.
灵活运用手中的银币招募英雄与士兵，获得最终的胜利吧！
Use the silver coins in your hands flexibly to recruit heroes and soldiers, and win the final victory!
返回
Return
是不是感觉敌军更多，更强了呢？
Do you feel that the enemy army is more and stronger?
将军大人不要担心，除了提升英雄和兵营等级以外，我们也有其他加强的手段哦！
Don't worry, besides raising the level of heroes and barracks, we also have other means of strengthening!
点击这里进入军魂界面
Click to enter Army Soul
八种军魂会从各个方向强化我军全体成员的战斗能力。
The eight Army Soul will strengthen the combat capabilities of army
请随意选择喜欢的方向进行强化吧！
Choose the direction you like to strengthen it!
之后的战斗就看将军大人的了！我会在旅途的终点恭候大人的！
Fighting! I will wait for you at the end of the journey!
哎呀，失败了呢，我们先回城增强下实力再来挑战吧！
Oops, it failed, let's go back to the city to strengthen our strength and then challenge again!
